{"id": 7768, "date": "2019-02-20T05:00:12", "date_gmt": "2019-02-20T13:00:12", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=7768"}, "modified": "2023-01-01T09:03:56", "modified_gmt": "2023-01-01T17:03:56", "slug": "cover-me-kt-tunstall-and-the-buena-vista-social-club-because-the-night", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/02/20/cover-me-kt-tunstall-and-the-buena-vista-social-club-because-the-night/", "title": {"rendered": "Cover Me, KT Tunstall and the Buena Vista Social Club: Because the Night"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>There are a\u00a0<em>lot</em> of &#8220;Because the Night&#8221; covers out there, but this is one of my favorites&#8211;and it comes from a most unexpected pairing.</p>\n<p>In 2009, The Buena Vista Social Club released their second album in their\u00a0<em>Rhythm del Mundo</em> series, in which they reinvent classic pop and rock songs by teaming up with US, UK, and Irish vocalists and backing them with a Cuban-infused instrumental track&#8211;all to raise funds and awareness for climate change and disaster relief.</p>\n<p>For &#8220;Because the Night,&#8221; they chose Scottish singer-songwriter KT Tunstall, and together, Tunstall and the BVSC found a Latin groove that highlights and enhances the sultriness of the lyrics (Patti Smith&#8217;s version, I should note) more than even Bruce&#8217;s original arrangement.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Rhythms Del Mundo feat. KT Tunstall - Because The Night\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/L8NZvg8qZTU?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p>(Alternate <a href=\"https://youtu.be/ETtF3UTNU3I\">source</a> if your country is blocked from the video above)</p>\n<p>Who&#8217;d have thunk: Jersey + Cuba + Scotland = magic.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>KT Tunstall and the Buena Vista Social Club bring out the sexy in their 2009 cover of &#8220;Because the Night.&#8221;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 7811, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [4], "tags": [415, 2206, 2205], "class_list": ["post-7768", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-cover-me", "tag-because-the-night", "tag-buena-vista-social-club", "tag-kt-tunstall"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/kttunstall.jpg?fit=500%2C500&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-21i", "jetpack_likes_enabled": true, "jetpack-related-posts": [{"id": 1009, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/03/12/roll-of-the-dice-kt-88/", "url_meta": {"origin": 7768, "position": 0}, "title": "Roll of the Dice: KT-88", "author": "Ken", "date": "March 12, 2018", "format": false, "excerpt": "We're in obscure territory today with this instrumental j